!! INTRODUCTION TO MORPHOLOGICAL ANALYSER OF ApurinГЈ LANGUAGE.
 

Multichar_Symbols  !!вүҲ # Definitions for @CODE@

!! ## Analysis symbols
!  ----------------
!! The morphological analyses of wordforms for the ApurinГЈ
!! language are presented in this system in terms of the following symbols.
!! (It is highly suggested to follow existing standards when adding new tags).

!! ## Tags for POS
 +A       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Adjective
 +Adp     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Adposition, i.e. Post- and Prepostion, NOT IN USE/ NГғO USADO
 +Adv     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Adverb
 +CC      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Conjunction
 +CS      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Subjunction
 +Interj  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Interjection
 +N       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Noun
 +Num     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Numeral
 +Pcle    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Particle
 +Po      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Postpostion
 +Pr      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Preposition
 +Pron    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Pronoun
 +Pers    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Personal Pronoun
 +V       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Verb

!! ## Tags for sub-POS
 +Arab      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Arabic numeral, subtag for +Num
 +Aux	    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Auxiliary
 +Coll      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Collective numerals, subtag for +N
 +Dem       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Demonstrative Pronoun
 +Fem 	    !!вүҲ	* **@CODE@** uwa
 +Indef     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Indefinitive Pronoun
 +Interr    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Interrogative Pronoun
 +Msc 	    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**  ywa
 +Pass      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +Pers      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Personal Pronoun
 +Prop      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Propernoun
 +Recipr    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Reciprocal Pronoun
 +Refl      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Reflexive Pronoun
 +Rel       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Relative Pronoun
 +Rom       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Roman numeral, subtag for +Num

 +Temp +Spat

!! # Tags for Inflection

!! ## Tags for Case and Number Inflection
 +Sg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Singular
 +Pl   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Plural

 +All  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** -mukary (allative)
 +Cau  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**	-xika 'because of'
 +Com  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Comitative -kata  (Assoc)
 +Dat  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Dative -munhi (allative)
 +Ill  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Illative
 +Loc  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Locative -ГЈ Locative (at, to), instrumental
 +Nom  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Nominative (morphological ZERO)
 +Prx  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** -takute 'in the proximity of'

 +Aff  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** affected by action of verb %>nhi
 +Cap  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 0 N>V capacity
 +Prp  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** ka- vido verbs from nouns
!!вүҲ	   -ka, -nhi

!! ## Possessive tags

 +PxSg1   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Singular First Person
 +PxSg2   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Singular Second Person
 +PxSg3F  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Singular Third Person Feminine
 +PxSg3M  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Singular Third Person Male
 +PxPl1   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Plural First Person
 +PxPl2   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Plural Second Person
 +PxPl3F  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Plural Third Person Feminine
 +PxPl3M  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Plural Third Person Male
 +NPossd  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** not possessed
 +Possd	  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Possessed

!! ## Adjectival tags

!! ## Tenses
 +Fut	!!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Future
 +NFut	!!вүҲ * **@CODE@** Non-Future

!! ## Verb person-number-gender

 +ScSg1 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation first person singular
 +ScSg2 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation second person singular
 +ScSg3F !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation third person singular Feminine
 +ScSg3M !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation third person singular Male
 +ScPl1 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation first person plural
 +ScPl2 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation second person plural
 +ScPl3F !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation third person plural Feminine
 +ScPl3M !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** subject conjugation third person plural Male

 +OcSg1 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation first person singular
 +OcSg2 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation second person singular
 +OcSg3F !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation third person singular Feminine
 +OcSg3M !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation third person singular Male
 +OcPl1 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation first person plural
 +OcPl2 !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation second person plural
 +OcPl3F !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation third person plural Feminine
 +OcPl3M !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** object conjugation third person plural Male

!! The Usage extents are marked using following tags:
 +Err/Orth
 +Err/Spellrelax ! used with nasalization marking
 +Use/-Spell 
  +Err/Orth-i-not-y !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**

!! The nominals are inflected in the following Case and Number

!! The comparative forms are:
 +Comp +Superl
!! Numerals are classified under:
 +Attr +Card
 +Ord 
!! Verb moods are:
 +Ind +Prs +Prt +Pot +Cond +Imprt
!! Verb personal forms are:
 +Sg1 +Sg2 +Sg3 +Pl1 +Pl2 +Pl3
 +Sc3M  +Sc3F
 +Oc3M  +Oc3F
 +Vido  !!вүҲ object formed intransitive descriptive
 +Vids  !!вүҲ subject formed intransitive descriptive

!! Other verb forms are
 +Inf +Ger +ConNeg +ConNegII +Neg +ImprtII +PrsPrc +PrfPrc +Sup +VGen +VAbess
 +Relzr-Subj !!= relativizer with subject reference kary/karu
 +Relzr-Obj  !!= relativizer with object reference kyty/kytu

 +Impf      !!= IPFTV
 +Perf      !!= PFTV perfective -pe


 +Pss	     !!= passivizer -~ka
 +Distr
+Caus
+Intr
+Augm
+TCaus
+Fact
+ColTV
+Prog	!!вүҲ * **@CODE@** nany
+Prog2	!!вүҲ * **@CODE@** na
+Prog3	!!вүҲ * **@CODE@** ГЈ (?= Loc)
+Almost
+Random
+Intens
+Des
+RS
+Vblz
+Hypoth
+Recipr
+Immin
+Caus
+Hab
+Pred !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = ka
+Frustr !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = ma: awa-pyty-ka-ma
+Emph	!!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = pyty: Ithu-pyty-ma-ry, IГЈu-pyty-ka-ry, ithu-pyty-ry

! Abbreviated words are classified with:
 +ABBR +ACR 
+Symbol !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = independent symbols in the text stream, like ВЈ, вӮ¬, В©
!! Special symbols are classified with:
+CLB +PUNCT +LEFT +RIGHT +MIDDLE
!! The verbs are syntactically split according to transitivity:
 +TV +IV
!! Special multiword units are analysed with:
 +Multi
!! Non-dictionary words can be recognised with:
 +Guess

!! Question and Focus particles:
 +Qst +Foc


!! ### Tags distinguishing different versions of the same lemma (before POS)
+v/iy !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** used to tag neutralized i/y and Д©/б»№ /usado para mostrar neutralidade de i/y e Д©/б»№
+v1   !!вүҲ * @CODE@
+v2   !!вүҲ * @CODE@
+v3   !!вүҲ * @CODE@
+v4   !!вүҲ * @CODE@
+v5   !!вүҲ * @CODE@
+v6   !!вүҲ * @CODE@
